text: vari pravaktalu varito (inka) ila annaru: "Niscayanga, memu mi vanti manavulam matrame! Kani allah tana dasulalo tanu korina varini anugrahistadu. Mariyu - allah anumatistene tappa - mi koraku pramanam tisuku ravatamanedi ma vasanlo ledu. Mariyu visvasulu kevalam allah midane drdhanam'makam uncukovalani
